careers.

21
00:01:33,372 --> 00:01:38,241
Exactly! [nods] Our brains are actually
wired for survival, which means they are

22
00:01:38,241 --> 00:01:42,926
built to quickly interpret feedback
through this personal lens. We make these

23
00:01:42,926 --> 00:01:47,363
lightning-fast, snap judgments about
whether this information is a threat

24
00:01:47,363 --> 00:01:52,356
before we’ve even had a second to reflect
on the actual intent behind the message.

25
00:01:53,039 --> 00:01:57,567
[thoughtful] That makes so much sense.
That psychological reality completely

26
